A couple in Statesville has been charged with child abuse after five children were found in unsanitary conditions in their home, along with the dead body of their grandfather.

Deputies said 25-year-old Melissa Kay Lynn Poole and 39-year-old Jeremy Daniel Dishner have been charged with misdemeanor child abuse.

Iredell County Sheriff Darren Campbell Campbell said the man's death was not suspicious.

